name: USS Enterprise 1701-D™
description: The NCC-1701-D™ is a 24th century starship in the Star Trek™ fictional universe and the setting of the Star Trek: The Next Generation™ television series. It's a Galaxy class ship and the fifth Federation starship in the Star Trek™ universe to carry the name Enterprise™. In most of its service the commanding officer of Enterprise D™ is Captain Jean-Luc Picard™.
